// from VPC-restricted access points (the latter resolve `vpc()` to the
// allowed `aws.vpc`), `bucketAccountId` shows the account that owns the
// underlying bucket, and `alias` exposes the access-point alias usable in
// place of the bucket name in S3 API calls.
private aws.s3.bucket.accessPoint @defaults("name networkOrigin") {
  // ARN of the access point
